* HP boosts are additive between Normal, Omega, and EX.
* Total HP boosts from weapon skills is capped at 400%
* {{itm|Broadsword of Earth}}'s "Titan's Aegis" weapon skill is not a standard "Aegis" skill and is not boostable by auras. Instead, it is a flat +50 per skill level (+500 HP at skill level 10).
